OL,3,C'Morpeth to Norfolk to Dorset (MND) -
OL,4,Criding 1,000km in memory of our dad'
OL,6,FTom Barton was in Morpeth to watch the
OL,7,Fcyclists set off for their 1,000
OL,8,Fkilometre trip to Dorset
OL,10,FA brother and sister are taking on a
OL,11,F1,000 kilometre charity challenge in
OL,12,Fmemory of their father who died from
OL,13,Fmotor neurone disease.
OL,15,FDaniel and Amy Smith and three of
OL,16,Ftheir friends set off on Monday (29
OL,17,FApril) from Morpeth, heading to
OL,18,FNorfolk and Dorset - places chosen to
OL,19,Fspell out MND.
