OL,3,C'Morpeth to Norfolk to Dorset (MND) -
OL,4,Criding 1,000km in memory of our dad'
OL,6,FThey are riding in memory of their
OL,7,Ffather, accountant Mark Smith, who
OL,8,Fdied last year after being diagnosed
OL,9,Fwith the condition which affects the
OL,10,Fbrain and nerves.
OL,12,FMark's daughter Amy told ITV Tyne
OL,13,FTees: "He'd think we were bonkers,
OL,14,Fwhich we are, probably. But he'd be so
OL,15,Fproud, and I think he'd be absolutely
OL,16,Fblown away by the support that we've
OL,17,Fgot. He'd be so happy. So he's with us
OL,18,F- in spirit."
