OL,3,C'Morpeth to Norfolk to Dorset (MND) -
OL,4,Criding 1,000km in memory of our dad'
OL,6,FHer bother Daniel said thinking of
OL,7,Ftheir father would be a "good
OL,8,Fmotivator" on their travels.
OL,10,F"If you're slightly in pain, it's
OL,11,Fnothing compared to what my dad and so
OL,12,Fmany others suffer," he added. "It
OL,13,Fdoes give you that boost - keeps you
OL,14,Fgoing."
OL,16,FIn his final months, Mark helped Amy
OL,17,Fand Daniel to put the trip together.
OL,19,FAnd driving the support van, and
OL,20,Fwatching her kids take on the
OL,21,Fchallenge, is Mark's widow Helen.
