OL,3,C'Morpeth to Norfolk to Dorset (MND) -
OL,4,Criding 1,000km in memory of our dad'
OL,6,FShe said: "They're doing an amazing
OL,7,Fjob in memory of their dad. (I'm) so
OL,8,Fproud."
OL,10,FThe group has already raised more than
OL,11,F#20,000 for the MND Association.
OL,13,FDominic McDonough, from the charity
OL,14,Fsaid: "I think it's an absolutely epic
OL,15,Fchallenge. I mean, my legs hurt just
OL,16,Fthinking about it.
OL,18,F"It's absolutely incredible and it
OL,19,Freally does mean so much to us at the
OL,20,Fcharity.
